{"tid":1991340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社運歌曲黎講，台灣既島嶼天光 定香港既願榮光歸香港？","createTime":"2020-04-27T11:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T11:29:00.000Z","uid":52658,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab2c6afd306276c4ad31d6ae14ff842b3d70955c","tid":1991340,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iV8JDbtXZm4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiV8JDbtXZm4&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4TH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=d905c644\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iV8JDbtXZm4</a><br />\n可能未必好多人知道呢首歌既意思<br />\n2014年<br />\n當時國民黨試圖強行通過極具爭議性既兩岸服貿協議<br />\n引發學生不滿 而發動佔領國會行動<br />\n<br />\n為期23日既佔領行動中<br />\n台灣警方既鎮暴隊多次以催淚瓦斯同水炮車驅趕群眾<br />\n當時滅火器樂團主音見到呢個場面<br />\n就寫左呢首歌 <br />\n代表著當時留守學生既心情<br />\n<br />\n呢場社運 被稱為太陽花革命<br />\n最終 服貿被迫撤回<br />\n次年大選 國民黨崩盤式大敗<br />\n而當時留守既學生 聯合創立左一個新政黨<br />\n即係而家既時代力量<br />\n<br />\n純粹以歌黎講 我覺得島嶼天光寫得好d啦<br />\n初初聽既時候 我係感動到想喊<br />\n但榮光就未到呢個程度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n島嶼天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2a02fcd14513d28f9f83eca2a0f383f1bdf5ab","tid":1991340,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:08:01.000Z","msg":"Bella ciao bella ciao Bella ciao ciao ciao <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0RPeoc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0RPeoc.png&h=558c0799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被起底警務人員：警方資助更換車牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913997</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca2fb3e00020f92071755166092cd3520284b20b","tid":1991340,"uid":67574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:08:23.000Z","msg":"榮光國歌黎喎<br />\n島嶼天光應該同返雙城記比較"},{"pid":"2c3e4ff74b1eafc2a